title: Chipotle's Sales Slowdown Leaves Investors Hungry For More
text:
Published By: Forbes.com: Latest News - Today 
Long the star of fast casual, Chipotle's same-store sales rose just 2.6% during the quarter, down sharply from 20% a year ago....
